Paper: hep-th/0104175

Date: 2001-04-20

Title: Black holes and conformal mechanics

Authors: S. Mignemi

Comments: 5 pages, plain TeX

Journal-ref: Mod.Phys.Lett. A16 (2001) 1997-2002

We show how the motion of a charged particle near the horizon of an extremeReissner-Nordstrom black hole can lead to different forms of conformalmechanics, depending on the choice of the time coordinate.